title: Sample Book, American Court Collection F., 1962
creditline: Gift of Katzenbach and Warren, Inc.
description: Sample book covered with wallpaper "The True Vine" (designed by William Justema), in orange, pink and drab on off-white, with orange cloth spine. The book contains sixteen handprinted designs.
